# Feature: Pet Profile + Local Partner Map

## Pet Profile
Stored in `guest.pets[]` — each pet has:
```typescript
interface PetProfile {
  id: string;
  name: string;
  species: "dog" | "cat" | "other";
  breed: string;
  weight_kg: number;
}
```

**Booking flow:** If guest has a pet profile AND the hotel is pet-friendly:
- Show "Bring [Pet Name]?" step in booking flow
- Display pet fee transparently (from hotel seed data)
- Store `booking.has_pet = true` on confirmation

**Hotel search:** When guest has an active pet profile, show:
- Pet-friendly filter chip in search results
- `PetFriendlyBadge` on matching hotel cards
- Pet weight limit check (warn if pet exceeds `hotel.pet_max_weight_kg`)

## Local Partner Map

### Mapbox Setup
- Token env var: `NEXT_PUBLIC_MAPBOX_TOKEN`
- Style: `mapbox://styles/mapbox/streets-v12`
- Initial view: hotel lat/lng, zoom 14
- Map component MUST be lazy-loaded with `dynamic(..., { ssr: false })`

### Partner Categories & Icons
| Category | Icon | Color |
|---|---|---|
| Vet (emergency) | 🏥 | red |
| Vet (regular) | 🐾 | orange |
| Dog walker / sitter | 🦮 | amber |
| Dog park | 🌳 | green |
| Pet-welcome restaurant | 🍽️ | purple |
| Pet supply store | 🛒 | blue |
| Bike rental | 🚲 | cyan |
| Vegan restaurant | 🥗 | lime |
| EV charging | ⚡ | yellow |
| Refill station | 💧 | sky |
| Local experience | 🎭 | indigo |

### Partner Seed Data Schema
```json
{
  "id": "partner-001",
  "hotel_id": "marriott-nyc-times-sq",
  "name": "Central Park Veterinary",
  "category": "vet_emergency",
  "lat": 40.7850,
  "lng": -73.9683,
  "address": "123 W 77th St, New York, NY",
  "phone": "+1-212-555-0123",
  "hours": "24/7",
  "rating": 4.8,
  "is_marriott_partner": true,
  "pet_relevant": true,
  "distance_km": 1.2
}
```

### Map Interactions
1. Category filter chips (horizontal scroll at top of map) — toggle on/off
2. Tap marker → bottom sheet slides up with `PartnerCard`
3. `PartnerCard` shows: name, distance, hours, rating, phone, "Get Directions" button
4. "Marriott Partner" gold badge on verified partners
5. Default: show all categories; if pet profile active, highlight pet-relevant by default

### Components
- `LocalPartnerMap` — main Mapbox wrapper (lazy-loaded)
- `PartnerCategoryFilter` — horizontal chip row
- `PartnerMarker` — custom colored marker by category
- `PartnerBottomSheet` — slide-up sheet on marker tap
- `PartnerCard` — card inside the bottom sheet
- `PetProfileForm` — used in profile page and booking flow
- `PetFriendlyBadge` — pill on hotel cards

### API Endpoints
`GET /hotels/{hotel_id}/partners?categories=vet,dog_park&lat=40.7&lng=-73.9`
`GET /guests/{guest_id}/pets` / `POST /guests/{guest_id}/pets` / `DELETE /guests/{guest_id}/pets/{pet_id}`
